snippet.title: Them's Fightin' Herds - Raw Gameplay video
snippet.description:
Them's Fightin' Herds: Crowdfund live now!

http://igg.me/at/ThemsFightinHerds

Disclaimer: The video does NOT include the Dynamic Music System, which is, as is the rest of the game, a work in progress. Video most likely won't be representative of the final state of the game (art assets will be finished, for once), so please don't take it as such.
